description: [``botocore``] The UserPoolType Status field is no longer used.
[``botocore``] Features : Adding support for new data ingestion source to Kinesis Firehose - AWS Managed Services Kafka.
[``botocore``] Added support for IoT Rules Engine Kafka Action Headers

[``botocore``] This release adds new feature - Layout to Analyze Document API which can automatically extract layout elements such as titles, paragraphs, headers, section headers, lists, page numbers, footers, table areas, key-value areas and figure areas and order the elements as a human would read.
